ts/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"真，最前明明嗌企鬆啲，去到中層就變慢慢退去到後排就個個馬拉松，前線回頭一望乜撚哂人"},{"pid":"23d550e73d4134a1813f2bf70d74e1b5f0fe6ffb","tid":1610220,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e99dc8451c2b3150acd91b83d9335be1fde986be","tid":1610220,"uid":3696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"今日嘅表現係71係合格嘅，但而家101啦大個啦好無"},{"pid":"0677deaf6ca7fbeb1a9bbf28d283ba6a32407e52","tid":1610220,"uid":25264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adfb67734f97b5eace635d738c5071daf6d009a9","tid":1610220,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39475a6a5d2cb599faffdba3f968608ed314031d","tid":1610220,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"我係喺灣仔嬲到喊嘅勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由海富老江湖勇武話上橋打狗<br />\n然後咩子彈都出<br />\n之後個個full gear偽勇武跑步快過保特<br />\n<br />\n淨返好少手足先無奈撤退<br />\n仲要一路撤到和昌大押行，嬲到喊<br />\n<br />\n夠人有得打都變冇得打，好灰<br />\n<br />\n偽勇武聽住呀，話我分化撚都要屌！<br />\n我哋嘅敵人唔止黑警、林鄭、政府，仲有成個中共<br />\n中共點屠殺自己睇返中史教科書<br />\n三面紅旗，三反五反，文革批鬥，八九六四<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡稱「冇底線」呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前光明頂入面陶傑冇講錯<br />\n「而家係要用搞革命嘅方式嚟爭取好卑微嘅訴求」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但有幾多人真係有搞革命嘅覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇呢種覺悟<br />\n我寧願你縮返後半gear又好和理非都好<br />\n個個見到full gear跑嘅個個都驚<br />\n製造埋哂啲不必要嘅恐慌<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係跑online呀，打仗呀！戰場呀！屌你老母！<br />\n揾次真係推，打狗好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"